My sweet Steph💜

From day one we clicked at new 42 studios. My tilt/leg sister, my nail day buddy and my Australian accent queen! We had such great times on and off the dance floor. You had such ferociousness to your dancing and such a sweet soul to all. A light put out too soon 😢 I will miss you tremendously but am glad you are not suffering any longer. You’re free to dance your heart out🕊 say hello to my brother @dblexicon for me and give him a big hug. We shall meet again at the gates of heaven. Until then, I will dance many dances for you 🙏🏾🕊#fuckcancer

I haven’t taken class in a while and this weekend I ended up taking 3 classes 😜 Monday classes can be hard because this is my only day off from work buuuutttt @justicemoore_  class gave me ALLLL the VIBES! I also got to dance with some bomb ass artist, including my sis and partner in crime @shonica 

 Thank you Justice for inspiring me to the max and getting this old body to move like I’m 19 again 🙏🏾 congrats on your first of many @stepsonbroadway  classes! 

Y’all get in her class next time!

A moment in time - @mjthemusical 
Thank you @erik_carter for the photo! Can’t wait to see the rest #smoothcriminal

My Dear Myles,

I am so grateful to have witnessed your impeccable work ethic, your beautiful heart on and off stage and your grace for yourself and for me! Being in a studio for two months straight, working one on one, was and will always be one of the highlights of my career! Congratulations on a run well done! I love you and can’t wait to continue to cheer you on my PG county brother! 

With love,
Kam
